skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: love guru
des:
Ask for love quotes, and learn what to say to your love, like I love you but in the better way.
To start, just say "Alexa, ask love guru" or " Alexa, tell love guru give me a love word. ".
At anytime, you can stop by saying " Alexa, tell love guru Thanks. " or " Alexa, tell love guru Nice. ".
You can get next quote by saying " Alexa, tell love guru tell me next. ".
And you can ask for help by saying " Alexa, ask love guru for help ".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
